{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"16545960996181147e":{"type":"custom-liquid","settings":{"custom_liquid":"","color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":36}},"165459444093b60ff6":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"16545944405e3d11aa-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Debate Venue","heading_size":"h1"}},"16545944405e3d11aa-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>In addition to being the accommodation partner, <br\/>Swiss-Belresort will also be the venue partner for this event. <\/p><p>All debates, seminars and meeting sessions will be taking place in the hotel.<\/p>"}},"16545944405e3d11aa-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","button_style_secondary":false}}},"block_order":["16545944405e3d11aa-0","16545944405e3d11aa-1","16545944405e3d11aa-2"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"background-1","full_width":true,"padding_top":32,"padding_bottom":32}},"1654596096e001469b":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"1654596095d74f938b-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Convening Hall","heading_size":"h2"}},"1654596095d74f938b-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Debaters will be able to congregate in a hall spacious enough to accommodate up to 200 participating debaters. The convening hall will be equipped with seats, projectors, and sound systems. <\/p><p><br\/>The covening hall is located within 1 minute's walk from the hotel's frontdesk. No early-morning commute to debate venues will be necessary.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"1654596095d74f938b-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["1654596095d74f938b-0","1654596095d74f938b-1","1654596095d74f938b-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BALLROOM_-_THEATRE.png","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"16545968467a7292de":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"16545968456f642f92-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Prep Area","heading_size":"h2"}},"16545968456f642f92-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The hotel's main lobby and its facilities will be available for debaters to use as prep areas. Teams will also be free to use the corridor spaces, poolside benches for their 15 minutes of intensive preparation.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"16545968456f642f92-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["16545968456f642f92-0","16545968456f642f92-1","16545968456f642f92-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/MAIN_LOBBY.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1654597199643d9070":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"1654597198510a0b7c-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Debate Rooms","heading_size":"h2"}},"1654597198510a0b7c-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Up to 25 hotel rooms will be retrofitted, redesigned, and utilized as debate rooms. The 36 sqm deluxe rooms will have their beds removed to fit tables and chairs required for the BP debate format. <\/p><p><br\/>This debate-in-hotel-room concept was excecuted by EduDrift in the 2017 edition of Asian BP in Krabi, and also in the 2019 edition of Australs here in Bali.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"1654597198510a0b7c-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["1654597198510a0b7c-0","1654597198510a0b7c-1","1654597198510a0b7c-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2019_07_02_IMG_0922_JPG.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1654597295f0f61f65":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"1654597295da2960b0-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Conference Rooms","heading_size":"h2"}},"1654597295da2960b0-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>To allow for more observers to witness the debates on-going, the outrounds of the tournament will be held in the hotel's conference rooms.<\/p><p><br\/>Quarter Finalist and Semi Finalists of the event can expect to debate in these spaces that can accommodate up to 30 spectators in each room.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"1654597295da2960b0-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["1654597295da2960b0-0","1654597295da2960b0-1","1654597295da2960b0-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/MEETING_ROOM-DOUBLE_U_SHAPE.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1654597640452e54d8":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"16545976408dbdb951-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Crowning the Asian Champions","heading_size":"h2"}},"16545976408dbdb951-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The Grand-Finals of the championship will be held in the hotel's Grand Ballroom to behold the glory of the next Asian Champions. <\/p><p><br\/>The Grand Finals will be followed by an award ceremony. Buffet will be served as we present the awards to participants of the event.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"16545976408dbdb951-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["16545976408dbdb951-0","16545976408dbdb951-1","16545976408dbdb951-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BALLROOM_-_ROUND_TABLE.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1654598025071974ba":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"1654598025d910bd37-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Poolside Welcome","heading_size":"h2"}},"1654598025d910bd37-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>To celebrate the milestones of debaters across Asia, participants will be welcomed with poolside drinks and enjoy nights of socialization.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"1654598025d910bd37-2":{"type":"button","disabled":true,"settings":{"button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["1654598025d910bd37-0","1654598025d910bd37-1","1654598025d910bd37-2"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_9382.jpg","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-1","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["main","16545960996181147e","165459444093b60ff6","1654596096e001469b","16545968467a7292de","1654597199643d9070","1654597295f0f61f65","1654597640452e54d8","1654598025071974ba"]}